              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "qa_important",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Soria",
            "text": "For now, just practice. When tools are available, start with a better cooler or backpack.\n\nYou can't make money if you can't carry your catch to market fresh!\n\nAfter that, specialize in what you love—fishing and processing.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "Tell me about gear and processing",
                "resultDialogId": "qa_kit_combined",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "General balancing advice?",
                "resultDialogId": "qa_advice",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Thanks, that helps! Goodbye",
                "resultDialogId": "qa_end",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "qa_advice",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Soria",
            "text": "Balance, sweetie. Don't pour all your coin into one thing.\n\nListen to the town—if Nash is worried about the fish, maybe ease up.\n\nIf Cassandra's begging for tilapia, maybe fish more. You're part of an ecosystem now.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "What gear should I focus on?",
                "resultDialogId": "qa_important",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Tell me about processing gear",
                "resultDialogId": "qa_kit_combined",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Thanks for the wisdom!",
                "resultDialogId": "qa_end",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "hello_response",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Soria",
            "text": "Hello! Always good to see a friendly face.\n\nNow, don't let me keep you! Those fish aren't going to catch themselves.\n\nCome back anytime!",
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "qa_end",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Soria",
            "text": "Good luck out there! Remember:\n\n• Practice makes perfect\n• Listen to the town\n• Balance is key\n\nMy door is always open when you need more advice!",
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [],
